# AI Solar Advisor — VS Code AI Build Prompts

Use these prompts **in order**, one at a time, inside VS Code's AI chat (Copilot Chat / Continue / whatever you have). Don't paste all at once — let it finish one phase, review the code, run it, THEN move to the next prompt. This keeps the AI focused and keeps you in control of understanding what's built.

